# ğŸ›ï¸ Ecommerce App (Kotlin + Firebase)

A modern, fully functional Android E-commerce application built with **Kotlin** and **Firebase**. This project demonstrates a professional **MVVM Architecture**, **Dependency Injection (Hilt)**, and real-time data handling.

It includes two distinct user roles: **Customer** (Shopping) and **Admin** (Product Management).

