## ğŸš€ Features

### ğŸ‘¤ Customer Features
* **Authentication:** Login, Sign Up, and Forgot Password (with OTP simulation).
* **Product Browsing:** View categories, search for products, and view detailed descriptions.
* **Shopping Cart:** Add/remove items, update quantities, and see real-time price calculations.
* **Wishlist:** Save favorite items for later.
* **Order Management:** Place orders and track status (Pending, Delivered, Canceled).
* **Profile:** Edit personal information and change password.

### ğŸ› ï¸ Admin Features
* **Dashboard:** Overview of products, orders, and users.
* **Product Management:** Add new products with images, update details, or delete items.
* **Order Management:** View all customer orders and change their status (e.g., mark as Shipped).

---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack & Architecture

* **Language:** [Kotlin](https://kotlinlang.org/) (100%)
* **Architecture:** MVVM (Model-View-ViewModel)
* **Dependency Injection:** [Dagger Hilt](https://dagger.dev/hilt/)
* **Asynchronous:** [Coroutines](https://kotlinlang.org/docs/coroutines-overview.html) & [Flow](https://kotlinlang.org/docs/flow.html)
* **Network & Database:** [Firebase Firestore](https://firebase.google.com/docs/firestore) & [Firebase Auth](https://firebase.google.com/docs/auth)
* **Navigation:** [Android Navigation Component](https://developer.android.com/guide/navigation) (Single Activity Architecture)
* **UI Components:** ViewBinding, Material Design, RecyclerView, DiffUtil.
* **Image Loading:** [Glide](https://github.com/bumptech/glide)

---

